Title: The Descent of Man
Plot: When a seasoned sky diver is paralyzed after free falling to earth when his parachute doesn't deploy, he turns out to be linked to the strange death-by-airborne-toxins of two wealthy men with ties to Iran.
GuestStars: David Berman, Liz Vassey, Charisma Carpenter, Erin Daniels, Greg Germann, Archie Kao, Eric Allan Kramer, Ivo Nandi, Joe Ochman, Charley Rossman, Larry Sullivan, Jon Wellner
